    public class SpringNamespaceHandler.SpringBeanFactoryBuilder.CoherenceApplicationContext
extends org.springframework.context.support.FileSystemXmlApplicationContext
    Application context implementation that supports Coherence expression macros within a Spring XML application context file. This allows injection of Coherence objects into a bean definition (such as {cache-name}).
    See Also:
